center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luc luong phe ve hoat dong ngang nhien ngay truoc khu vuc ban ve cua BTC san Thien Truong.\" title=\"L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng phe v\u00e9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngang nhi\u00ean ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khu v\u1ef1c b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a BTC s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/e-am-phe-ve-bua-vay-ban-ban-ve-cua-btc-san-thien-truong.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng phe v\u00e9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngang nhi\u00ean ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khu v\u1ef1c b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a BTC s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi CLB TP.HCM t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 5, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 t\u1eebng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf tr\u0103n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u00e9o kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n, khi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ee9c x\u00fac khi BTC ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh tay v\u1edbi n\u1ea1n &quot;phe v\u00e9&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Theo ghi nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a PV Bongda24h.vn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hai gi\u1edd, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng &quot;phe v\u00e9&quot; v\u1eabn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khu v\u1ef1c b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a BTC s\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 do s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m \u0111i sau nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 ch\u1ee3 \u0111en c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u1ebf \u1ea9m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i v\u00e9 &quot;ch\u1ee3 \u0111en&quot; ch\u1ec9 t\u0103ng kho\u1ea3ng 5.000 - 10.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng so v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 ni\u00eam y\u1ebft c\u1ee7a BTC. C\u00e0ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, do v\u1eabn c\u00f2n &quot;\u00f4m&quot; nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e9, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 phe v\u00e9 m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ngang b\u1eb1ng so v\u1edbi BTC \u0111\u1ec3... thu h\u1ed3i v\u1ed1n.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>D\u00f9 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c phe v\u00e9 b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a BTC v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 phe v\u00e9 ngang nhi\u00ean v\u00e0o t\u1eadn b\u00e0n b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a BTC \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs TP HCM:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luong nguoi ham mo den san Thien Truong mua ve truoc tran khong nhieu.\" title=\"L\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng mua v\u00e9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/IMG_7995.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>L\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng mua v\u00e9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phe ve con den sat ban ban ve cua BTC de moi chao nguoi ham mo.\" title=\"Phe v\u00e9 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e1t b\u00e0n b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a BTC \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/IMG_8000_resize.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>Phe v\u00e9 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e1t b\u00e0n b\u00e1n v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a BTC \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac CDV nhiet thanh cua Nam Dinh dan ham nong bau khong khi tai san Thien Truong.\" title=\"C\u00e1c C\u0110V nhi\u1ec7t th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh d\u1ea7n h\u00e2m n\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/IMG_8005_resize.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>C\u00e1c C\u0110V nhi\u1ec7t th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh d\u1ea7n h\u00e2m n\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\