da24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-13-juventus-hut-chet-tren-san-nha-184-184064.html\">tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 non kinh nghi\u1ec7m, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh cho \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver, 33 tu\u1ed5i, m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c UEFA x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng ng\u0169 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u01b0u t\u00fa h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t, qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc cho v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 80 n\u0103m <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/ben-le-world-cup/world-cup-2018-tai-nga-quay-cuong-giua-am-muu-va-de-doa-440-183162.html\">v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng c\u00e1c v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver \u0111\u00e3, \u0111ang v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00f3 qu\u00ean trong \u0111\u00eam Bernabeu v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u00f2n h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m an \u1ee7i d\u00e0nh cho \u00f4ng \u2013 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trong tai Michael Oliver Ban linh cua tuoi tre hinh anh 4\" title=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Trong-tai-Michael-Oliver-Ban-linh-cua-tuoi-tre-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e3y nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh, gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0 d\u01a1, m\u00e1u m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n uy. Hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao n\u00e0o m\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, t\u1eeb Buffon, Chiellini, Barzagli v\u00e0 Lichtsteiner c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn Ronaldo v\u00e0 Modric c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c (k\u00e9o theo kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh) v\u1ed1n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c UEFA c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc cho nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out Champions League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, n\u1ebfu <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-juventus-03-real-madrid-gioi-han-nao-cho-ken-ken-trang-184-183492.html\">k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i \u1edf Turin kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f4ng-c\u00f3-v\u1ebb an b\u00e0i</span> nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn tay tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i sau 45 ph\u00fat ti\u1ebfp theo: <em><strong>\u201cH\u1eafn ta l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n s\u00e1t nh\u00e2n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tr\u00e1i tim c\u1ee7a h\u1eafn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i th\u00f9ng r\u00e1c b\u1ea9n th\u1ec9u kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m.\u201d</strong></em> \u2013 C\u00e2u l\u1eddi ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Gianluigi Buffon. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cH\u1eafn ta th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t m\u1ed9t l\u1ed7i do ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra.\u201d \u2013 Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfp. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trong tai Michael Oliver Ban linh cua tuoi tre hinh anh 4\" title=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Gianluigi-Buffon-and-Michael-Oliver.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gigi Buffon x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m, ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Hai quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm g\u00ec v\u1edbi Champions League. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 tham gia c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i nay r\u1ed3i, v\u1edbi ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Juventus tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sporting Lisbon \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich tr\u01b0\u1edbc Besiktas \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u1edf Bernabeu, n\u01a1i \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi hai quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i nhau.</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd sau khi Medhi Benatia lao ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o l\u01b0ng Lucas Vazquez cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e0m tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean quan s\u00e1t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u0169ng c\u1ea3m, li\u1ec1u l\u0129nh v\u00e0 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u00f3 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver ch\u01b0a xong \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y khi \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1eefa mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t s\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trong tai Michael Oliver Ban linh cua tuoi tre hinh anh 4\" title=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Trong-tai-Michael-Oliver-Ban-linh-cua-tuoi-tre-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver kh\u00f4ng l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Buffon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ee7a v\u00e2y b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng ph\u00e2n tr\u1ea7n, ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdi s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi. \u00d4ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c quay ngo\u1eaft ra \u0111\u1eb1ng sau \u0111\u1ec3 nghi\u1ec7m xem c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea9y vai \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra, truy x\u00e9t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p n\u00e0o h\u1ebft, ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng la h\u00e9t \u0111i\u00ean cu\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver c\u1ee7a Buffon \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 gi\u00e1c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. L\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng tu\u1ed5i t\u1ee9 tu\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111ang <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-chung-ket-champions-league-tren-doi-tay-cua-ke-ve-nhi-vi-dai-184-112720.html\">ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span> xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i \u00e1o s\u1ed1 23 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rio Ferdinand mong m\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u201cl\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n, n\u00ean th\u01a1 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u00ecnh\u201d khi Buffon \u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 penalty c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec Gary Lineker cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \u201cM\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111au l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 tan n\u00e1t tr\u00e1i tim.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i tay c\u1ee7a Buffon x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u00ean vai m\u00ecnh, \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 hi\u1ec3u m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i qu\u00e1 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n cho ph\u00e9p. Va ch\u1ea1m v\u1eadt l\u00fd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t b\u1eb1ng th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, c\u1ee9 theo lu\u1eadt m\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u00f9 c\u00f3 t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh rong ru\u1ed5i ki\u1ebfm t\u00ecm vinh quang Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trong tai Michael Oliver Ban linh cua tuoi tre hinh anh 4\" title=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/trong-tai-tang-pen-cho-real-duoc-ca-ngoi-hay-nhat-nuoc-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver - B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u1ee9ng danh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang, v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang, l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng hay ho t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juve, c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 C\u0110V \u2013 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i, ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed mi\u1ec7t th\u1ecb v\u00e0 x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m nh\u01b0 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t Buffon \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i \u2013 \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng\u2026 ch\u1ea5p, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh kh\u00f3 tin so v\u1edbi tu\u1ed5i ngh\u1ec1 v\u00e0 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng Howard Webb v\u00e0 Matt Clattenburg, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfm t\u00ecm ra v\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/vi-sao-trong-tai-anh-vang-mat-tai-vck-world-cup-2018-421-183409.html\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span>, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u1edf Qatar sau \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i ra sao trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/trong-tai-tang-pen-cho-real-duoc-ca-ngoi-hay-nhat-nuoc-anh-184-184170.html\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i t\u1eb7ng pen cho Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i hay nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ong-ta-la-ke-giet-nguoi-mau-lanh-ke-khong-co-trai-tim-184-184070.html\">H\u1eafn ta l\u00e0 k\u1ebb gi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e1u l\u1ea1nh, k\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1i tim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/si-va-trong-tai-buffon-bi-dan-anh-giao-huan-184-184123.html\">S\u1ec9 v\u1ea3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, Buffon b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0n anh gi\u00e1o hu\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articler