ck;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Gareth Bale b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Bale r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh b\u1ecb thay ra ch\u1ec9 sau 45 ph\u00fat trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale cua Real\" title=\"Gareth Bale cua Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/inter-milan-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-sao-bu-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real Madrid khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Ph\u00eda Los Blancos c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin Bale chia tay Real \u0111ang r\u1ed9 l\u00ean th\u00ec Daily Mail l\u1ea1i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBale tin t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Zidane \u0111\u01b0a m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec Bale</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Bale tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid</strong></span> \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Bayern Munich v\u00e0 PSG ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bale l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zinedine Zidane phat bieu ve Gareth Bale\" title=\"Zinedine Zidane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/zidane-giai-thich-ly-do-rut-bale-ra-nghi-o-tran-gap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gareth Bale</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd M.U v\u00e0 Tottenham m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng bu\u1ed3n nh\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu Bale \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid, b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League n\u1ebfu chia tay Real, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Daily Mail, d\u00f9 Bale tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00ec M.U v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Los Blancos \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Hazard ho\u1eb7c Salah, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd nh\u1ea3 Bale l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao M.U, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/rio-ferdinand-muon-mu-chieu-mo-sao-real-madrid-172-184095.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Rio Ferdinand mu\u1ed1n M.U mua Bale</strong></span>, theo c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/15354-42556/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1180","checkdouble":"184223"},{"date":"14:34 14/04","title":"Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Real mua sao Valencia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/ronaldo-muon-real-mua-sao-valencia.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.arti