1b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 8 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 20 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap &ldquo;B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i&rdquo; \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean BXH.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Goncalo-Guedes.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Guedes \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Valencia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Goncalo Guedes c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Valencia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Valencia \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2017 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb PSG. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996, &ldquo;B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i&rdquo; \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Real \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Goncalo Guedes</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Valencia mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 khi m\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real </strong></span>v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c. Theo Don Balon, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111ang th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Real Madrid mua Goncalo Guedes \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo muon Real Madrid mua Goncalo Guedes hinh anh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Real Madrid mua Goncalo Guedes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/ronaldo-muon-real-mua-sao-valencia.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Real mua Goncalo Guedes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nSi\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. CR7 mu\u1ed1n Los Blancos chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Ronaldo, Real kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Harry Kane hay Robert Lewandowski, b\u1edfi CR7 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRonaldo mu\u1ed1n Real \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Goncalo Guedes l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. Ngo\u00e0i Real th\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Valencia. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/arsenal-nham-goncalo-guedes-184-175086.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Guedes</strong></span>, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mirror \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Goncalo Guedes kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, anh s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real Madrid mua Goncalo Guedes th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Goncalo Guedes \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/280979-42556/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Goncalo Guedes \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1179","checkdouble":"184224"},{"date":"15:21 14/04","ti