f3ng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 8 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma 3-0 Barca\" title=\"Roma 3-0 Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/roma-30-barca-thay-hen-nhat-tro-tra-gia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Barca b\u1ecb Roma lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Camp Nou, Barca \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roma trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1. Roma \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Barca 3-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-roma-vs-barca-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-183967.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Roma vs Barca </strong></span>khi\u1ebfn t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn l\u00e0 4-4, nh\u01b0ng Roma \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd lu\u1eadt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Messi r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roma</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Valverde n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Messi, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roma.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi co the mat bong vang la he qua sau tran thua cua Barca\" title=\"Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/hlv-barca-messi-rat-buon-vi-bi-loai-khoi-champions-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Barca, Messi t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u00fat ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Messi, t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y. Barca v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft C\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i La Liga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/12994-42556/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1178","checkdouble":"184229"},{"date":"16:35 14/04","title":"Diego Costa c\u00f3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Arsenal?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/diego-costa-co-kip-bun