style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Costa chan thuong, Arsenal mung tham hinh anh\" title=\"Diego Costa ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Arsenal m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/diego-costa-co-kip-bung-phuc-de-doi-dau-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Diego Costa ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Europa League nh\u01b0ng Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eaft. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-tra-gia-cuc-dat-sau-tam-ve-vao-ban-ket-europa-league-180-184139.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Diego Costa ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</strong></span>. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Torres \u1edf ph\u00fat 52.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Costa g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 v\u00e0 NHM Atletico Madrid r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng, b\u1edfi l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Diego Costa ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00eda Atletico Madrid k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn Costa ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng anh \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong hai tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Costa chan thuong\" title=\"Diego Costa ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/atletico-madrid-tra-gia-cuc-dat-sau-tam-ve-vao-ban-ket-europa-league.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Diego Costa ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Atletico vi\u1ebft: \u201cCosta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sporting. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. Sau \u0111\u00f3 Costa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 6, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo tr\u00e1i, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c cho hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League hay kh\u00f4ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAtletico \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Arsenal s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm \u1edf Europa League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng xem. Atletico Madrid s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 26/4, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng Costa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Diego Costa \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/21212-42556/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Diego Costa \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1177","checkdouble":"184234"},{"date":"16:41 14/04","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Barca vs Valencia 21h15 ng\u00e0y 14/4 (La Liga 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/truc-tiep-barca-vs-valencia-21h15-ngay-144-la-liga-201718.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margi