orner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giroud d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0110\u00f4ng 2018 n\u0103m nay, Arsenal b\u1ecf ra 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Aubameyang t\u1eeb Dortmund. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon, s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Wenger c\u00f3 3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Aubameyang, Lacazette v\u00e0 Giroud.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roi Arsenal, Olivier Giroud phat bieu ve Chelsea hinh anh\" title=\"R\u1eddi Arsenal, Olivier Giroud ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Roi-Arsenal,-Olivier-Giroud-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Giroud ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t Giroud \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nOlivier Giroud ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea</strong></span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi anh r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge. Chelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Arsenal trong v\u00f2ng 6 n\u0103m, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed th\u00e1ch \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u01a1i th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Giroud quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Chelsea, Giroud s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Alvaro Morata. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olivier Giroud phat bieu ve Chelsea hinh anh 2\" title=\"Olivier Giroud ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/giroud-quyet-dinh-roi-arsenal-den-chelsea-voi-toi-rat-de-dang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Giroud quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201c\u1ede nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u1eefa t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Morata t\u1ed1t cho c\u1ea3 2. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Eden Hazard, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh h\u01a1n, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Southampton \u1edf v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League, mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Top 4 h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1175","checkdouble":"184230"},{"date":"14:48 14/04","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Southampton vs Chelsea 18h30 ng\u00e0y 14/4 (Premier League 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/truc-tiep-southampton-vs-chelsea-18h30-ngay-144-premier-league-201718.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font