xt-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roberto Firmino chan thuong HLV Klopp len tieng hinh anh\" title=\"Roberto Firmino ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng HLV Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/klopp-len-tieng-ve-chan-thuong-cua-firmino.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roberto Firmino ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf c\u1ed5</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City, Roberto Firmino ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf c\u1ed5 v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thay ra. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn NHM The Kop t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y Firmino l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Liverpool, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Salah v\u00e0 Mane h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Firmino</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Bournemouth, HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/roberto-firmino-54460.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Firmino </strong></span>ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ed5 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp\" title=\"HLV Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/HLV-Klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Firmino</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf c\u1ed5 trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Etihad. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bournemouth. Firmino r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ragnar Klavan v\u00e0 Nathaniel Clyne nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Bournemouth \u1edf v\u00f2ng 34 Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Klavan d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 quan. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bournemouth\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Clyne c\u0169ng v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ngay sau khi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1173","checkdouble":"184233"},{"date":"17:16 14/04","title":"Vincent Kompany: \"3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn Man City\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/vincent-kompany-3-that-bai-lien-tiep-khong-anh-huong-den-man-city.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.a