l(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111ang ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Man xanh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kha nang Man City vo dich Premier League dang bi nghi ngo\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League \u0111ang b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/man-city-van-co-the-mat-chuc-vo-dich-premier-league-mua-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y khi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/man-city-1471.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City</strong></span> \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-5 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. \u1ede Premier League, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u1ec3 M.U r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1eabn l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Man City s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Tottenham. 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Man xanh ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Spurs, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kompany tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Man City s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/vincent-kompany-44156.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Vincent Kompany</strong></span> ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u1ee7a Man xanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vincent Kompany phat bieu ve Man City\" title=\"Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/vincent-kompany-3-that-bai-lien-tiep-khong-anh-huong-den-man-city.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Man City kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Man City s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Man City trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Man City \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Premier League&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, Man City x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Kompany \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/6019-40942/033100\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Kompany \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1172","checkdouble":"184238"},{"date":"17:13 14/04","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Liverpool vs Bournemouth 23h30 ng\u00e0y 14/4 (Premier League 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/truc-tiep-liverpool-vs-bournemouth-23h30-ngay-144-premier-league-201718.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3