rgin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 5 V-League 2018 di\u1ec5n ra cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, CLB HAGL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i BXH, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. M\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 4 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng khi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xuan Truong noi gi truoc tran dau o vong 5 V-League hinh anh\" title=\"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 5 V-League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/xuan-truong-khong-lo-hagl-bi-suy-yeu-vi-thieu-tuan-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9, CLB HAGL \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, sau 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng tin v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee7 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 toan t\u00ednh thay th\u1ebf ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. Tinh th\u1ea7n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, hy v\u1ecdng HAGL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC\u201d, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u2018h\u00edp\u2019 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc qu\u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. \u201cV\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00e1n k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs HAGL s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i nay 14/4 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1168","checkdouble":"184209"},{"date":"10:55 14/04","title":"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1ea1t sao Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/7/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-tiep-tuc-gat-sao-viet-kieu-khoi-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom