d-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gi\u1ea3i U19 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu U19 Suwon JS Cup s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 18 t\u1edbi 22/4 t\u1edbi.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>Trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 24 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u Tony L\u00ea Tu\u1ea5n Anh.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tony Tuan Anh bi loai khoi U19 Viet Nam hinh anh\" title=\"Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-che-sao-viet-kieu-trong-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i C\u1ed9ng h\u00f2a S\u00e9c t\u1eebng xin t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng \u0110T U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng do anh g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Tu\u1ea5n Anh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy v\u1eady, sau g\u1ea7n hai tu\u1ea7n qua, sao Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, n\u00ean HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 6 c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i Tr\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Minh - c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t VCK U19 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng U19 \u0110\u1ed3ng Th\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 Qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m m\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u00ec PVF.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn C\u00f4ng Minh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Ph\u1ea1m V\u0103n Nam, T\u1ed1ng V\u0103n H\u1ee3p, Tr\u1ea7n Ti\u1ebfn Anh v\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u00e1i Hi\u1ebfu do ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/4. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi&nbsp;c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 Mexico v\u00e0 U19 Ma-r\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Tu\u1ea5n Anh t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c:</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Y Eli Ni\u00ea, Nguy\u1ec5n Nh\u1eadt Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n T\u1edbi, B\u00f9i Ho\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Anh, Nguy\u1ec5n Xu\u00e2n Ki\u00ean, Th\u00e1i B\u00e1 Sang, Nguy\u1ec5n Ho\u00e0ng Duy, Nguy\u1ec5n Duy Ki\u00ean, Mai S\u1ef9 Ho\u00e0ng</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, L\u00ea V\u0103n Xu\u00e2n (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i), Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng, Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh, \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u1eafm, Ph\u1ea1m V\u0103n Lu\u00e2n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Nh\u00e2m M\u1ea1nh D\u0169ng, L\u00ea Minh B\u00ecnh, L\u00ea Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa.</p>\r\n<h3>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Suwon JS Cup:<o:p></o:p></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&nbsp;18/4/2018</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">14h00: Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Mexico <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">17h00: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Ma-r\u1ed1c<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&nbsp;20/4/2018</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">15h00: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">18h00: Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Ma-r\u1ed1c<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&nbsp;22/4/2018</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">13h00: Ma-r\u1ed1c vs Mexico<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">16h00: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Vi\u1ec7t Nam<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#081F2C;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThanh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1167","checkdouble":"184211"}]}